WEBVTT

00:12.240 --> 00:14.800
(I was born in Luoying Valley.)

00:15.240 --> 00:17.000
(We are a respected, righteous sect)

00:17.000 --> 00:18.600
(founded by Founder Beichen.)

00:18.960 --> 00:21.070
(Yet the women in the valley bear)

00:21.070 --> 00:22.230
(the curse of the demoness.)

00:23.800 --> 00:25.640
(The first one lived alongside beasts.)

00:27.030 --> 00:29.280
(The second one eloped with villains.)

00:30.120 --> 00:32.350
(The third one obsessed over poisons.)

00:33.240 --> 00:35.520
(My aunt Cai Pingshu, the fourth one,)

00:35.840 --> 00:37.280
(was finally not a demoness.)

00:37.920 --> 00:40.390
(Yet Nie Hengcheng,
Chief of the Li Sect,)

00:40.670 --> 00:41.740
(bathed Jianghu in blood.)

00:50.840 --> 00:53.280
(To save the Six Sects of Beichen
from danger,)

00:54.000 --> 00:56.750
(my aunt rushed
to Mount Tu with her blade)

00:57.070 --> 00:58.840
(to fight against Nie Hengcheng.)

01:08.300 --> 01:10.420
(Cai Pingshu, Luoying Valley)

01:10.460 --> 01:11.960
(Nie Hengcheng, Chief of the Li Sect)

01:47.120 --> 01:48.600
(In the end, she killed the villain)

01:49.040 --> 01:50.280
(at the cost of her life.)

02:02.000 --> 02:03.000
(Everyone says)

02:03.200 --> 02:05.040
(she was a legendary heroine.)

02:06.040 --> 02:08.030
(But I only saw her lingering
on a sickbed)

02:08.280 --> 02:09.870
(on the verge of death.)

02:15.779 --> 02:17.419
(I do not want
to repeat the tragic fate)

02:17.430 --> 02:18.870
(of the women of Luoying Valley.)

02:19.560 --> 02:21.630
(I only like a life of food, drinks,)

02:21.630 --> 02:23.470
(and storybooks.)

02:24.520 --> 02:25.360
(But the world)

02:25.870 --> 02:27.800
(does not offer such ease.)

02:45.080 --> 02:46.190
(Later,)

02:46.750 --> 02:48.910
(when I walked their paths they walked,)

02:49.680 --> 02:50.910
(I finally realized)

02:51.800 --> 02:53.030
(that it was)

02:54.030 --> 02:54.870
(not a curse,)

02:57.310 --> 02:58.310
(but fate.)

03:00.220 --> 03:03.540
=Generation to Generation=

03:03.620 --> 03:06.540
=Episode 1=

03:07.060 --> 03:09.620
(Luoying Valley)

03:14.800 --> 03:16.840
Everyone's here to see me off today.

03:18.870 --> 03:21.120
The thought of not seeing you all
for a whole year

03:21.680 --> 03:23.280
truly breaks my heart.

03:23.900 --> 03:25.313
(Cai Zhao, Luoying Valley)
I may be

03:25.324 --> 03:26.280
traveling far,

03:26.320 --> 03:27.170
but my heart

03:27.190 --> 03:28.859
will always stay with you.

03:28.870 --> 03:30.272
(Ingenious Scholar, Luoying Valley)

03:30.283 --> 03:31.430
During my absence,

03:31.630 --> 03:33.590
you must uphold my aunt's wishes.

03:34.360 --> 03:35.910
Whether it's taverns, shops, inns,

03:35.910 --> 03:37.656
or tooth parlors, pawnshops,
and bathhouses,

03:38.080 --> 03:39.630
be fair to all,

03:39.870 --> 03:40.883
and strive for excellence,

03:41.360 --> 03:43.560
so that every traveler from Jianghu...

03:43.910 --> 03:45.590
May they come with delight

03:45.800 --> 03:47.680
and leave satisfied.

03:50.150 --> 03:51.120
Manager Zhao,

03:51.560 --> 03:54.170
- we'll all miss you.
- Yes.

03:54.190 --> 03:56.030
However, that's the rule.

03:56.190 --> 03:57.180
Even if we hate to part,

03:58.000 --> 03:58.800
we must.

03:58.860 --> 04:00.100
(Cai Han, Luoying Valley)
No.

04:00.120 --> 04:01.750
We've finally grown prosperous.

04:01.960 --> 04:02.900
With business thriving,

04:03.240 --> 04:04.220
we can't give up halfway.

04:05.280 --> 04:06.590
For the glorious future

04:06.590 --> 04:08.150
of every street, alley, and shop,

04:09.080 --> 04:09.920
I've decided:

04:11.310 --> 04:12.430
I won't go to Qingque Sect.

04:12.960 --> 04:14.310
Han, let's go home.

04:14.310 --> 04:15.150
You must go.

04:16.360 --> 04:18.570
- Study comes first.
- Yes.

04:18.600 --> 04:19.920
Study is more important.

04:19.990 --> 04:20.510
Manager Zhao,

04:20.521 --> 04:21.830
please travel with peace of mind.

04:21.830 --> 04:24.160
Farewell, Manager Zhao.

04:24.160 --> 04:26.180
(All the Best, Bright Future)
I won't go.

04:26.270 --> 04:27.310
Farewell, Manager Zhao.

04:27.310 --> 04:28.720
I won't go.

04:28.720 --> 04:29.600
- Farewell.
- Go.

04:29.600 --> 04:31.950
I don't want to learn.

04:32.070 --> 04:35.680
Farewell, Manager Zhao.

04:35.680 --> 04:38.070
I won't go.

04:40.120 --> 04:42.630
I won't go.

04:45.700 --> 04:47.940
(Ning Xiaofeng, Lady of Luoying Valley)

04:47.980 --> 04:50.180
(Cai Pingchun, Lord of Luoying Valley)

04:50.360 --> 04:51.840
Go, don't dawdle.

04:57.420 --> 04:59.590
Mother!

05:03.870 --> 05:07.500
Farewell, Manager Zhao.

05:07.500 --> 05:09.500
(Luoying Valley)
Farewell, Manager Zhao.

05:09.500 --> 05:12.830
Farewell, Manager Zhao.

05:13.800 --> 05:15.240
Zhao, don't be upset.

05:15.630 --> 05:17.560
Sending disciples
to Qingque Sect for a year

05:17.800 --> 05:19.466
is a tradition
of the Six Sects of Beichen

05:19.600 --> 05:20.866
for over 200 years.

05:21.240 --> 05:22.240
Mother,

05:23.160 --> 05:25.000
I can't adapt to life outside.

05:26.430 --> 05:28.510
I just like staying home.

05:28.893 --> 05:31.053
Your three-year mourning period
for your aunt is over.

05:31.510 --> 05:33.000
Even if the sky falls today,

05:33.560 --> 05:35.160
you must go to Qingque Sect.

05:36.360 --> 05:37.750
If you act so recklessly again,

05:37.920 --> 05:39.360
you'll surely cause a great disaster.

05:39.600 --> 05:41.240
As a sheltered noble lady,

05:41.240 --> 05:42.080
I don't even know

05:42.240 --> 05:43.870
everyone in Jianghu.

05:44.100 --> 05:45.360
How could I cause trouble there?

05:47.950 --> 05:48.790
Zhao,

05:48.800 --> 05:50.240
just treat it as going

05:50.430 --> 05:51.590
through the motions, okay?

05:52.630 --> 05:54.070
Learning martial arts at Qingque Sect

05:54.680 --> 05:56.040
is your aunt's final wish.

05:56.950 --> 05:57.950
You decide for yourself.

06:02.190 --> 06:03.070
Aunt,

06:03.390 --> 06:04.720
I won't join Jianghu.

06:04.800 --> 06:06.240
Can I not train?

06:06.510 --> 06:07.360
Six parts talent,

06:07.630 --> 06:08.510
four parts practice.

06:09.310 --> 06:10.150
When you grow up,

06:10.600 --> 06:12.120
you'll have to rely on yourself.

06:12.422 --> 06:14.448
(Young Cai Zhao, Luoying Valley)
Outside Jianghu,

06:14.680 --> 06:16.630
you still have to be able
to protect yourself.

06:30.390 --> 06:31.840
Milord, a pigeon message.

06:31.840 --> 06:34.540
(Bandits attack; go to Chang Fort)

06:34.540 --> 06:36.580
(10 hours earlier, Chang Fort)

06:47.820 --> 06:50.580
(Chang Ning, Chang Fort)

06:50.980 --> 06:53.340
(Chang Haosheng, Lord of Chang Fort)

07:33.390 --> 07:36.950
- Chang?
- Chang!

07:37.510 --> 07:38.680
Chang!

07:39.870 --> 07:40.710
Don't come closer.

07:42.423 --> 07:43.849
We are the Cais from Luoying Valley.

07:44.630 --> 07:46.000
Calm down. We won't hurt you.

07:48.160 --> 07:49.240
Calm down.

07:49.310 --> 07:50.150
Don't come closer.

07:51.240 --> 07:52.590
Stay calm.

07:55.750 --> 07:57.200
Calm down.

08:13.830 --> 08:15.110
Zhao, don't hurt him.

08:24.190 --> 08:25.040
Uncle Qi?

08:25.220 --> 08:28.340
(Qi Yunke, Lord of Qingque Sect)

08:37.610 --> 08:38.670
Be gentle.

08:39.440 --> 08:40.390
How careless.

08:41.510 --> 08:43.150
He stayed by Chang's body

08:43.750 --> 08:44.630
all night

08:45.270 --> 08:46.510
and fought through the night.

08:47.750 --> 08:48.600
We came too late.

08:52.270 --> 08:53.360
(Please take care)

08:53.826 --> 08:54.966
(of Chang Ning, my only son.)

08:55.790 --> 08:58.600
(I'd be always grateful.)

09:27.390 --> 09:28.250
Yunke.

09:28.270 --> 09:29.110
Mr. Cai.

09:29.282 --> 09:30.695
I've checked the surrounding bodies.

09:30.706 --> 09:32.259
(Li Wenxun, Qingque Sect)
20 in total.

09:32.270 --> 09:33.910
From their weapons and clothing,

09:34.166 --> 09:35.332
their identities are unknown,

09:35.840 --> 09:37.600
but from the marks on their palms,

09:37.963 --> 09:39.200
they are all trained assassins.

10:25.120 --> 10:25.960
Run!

11:14.550 --> 11:15.790
He's heavily wounded,

11:15.993 --> 11:16.960
internal power depleted,

11:18.030 --> 11:20.550
and poisoned
with at least five rare toxins.

11:20.670 --> 11:21.910
Our Yudu Powder

11:22.200 --> 11:23.040
won't work?

11:23.120 --> 11:24.360
After such a desperate battle,

11:24.463 --> 11:25.750
the poison has entered the lungs.

11:26.200 --> 11:27.150
Our sect has medicine.

11:28.030 --> 11:29.440
I'll take him back to heal.

11:30.840 --> 11:32.200
I'll leave the rest to you.

11:35.180 --> 11:39.860
(Grave of Mr. Chang Haosheng)

11:45.000 --> 11:45.840
Father,

11:46.080 --> 11:47.630
should we avenge Uncle Chang?

11:47.840 --> 11:49.390
We must.

11:49.910 --> 11:51.320
It is the elders' matter.

11:52.120 --> 11:54.510
Uncle Chang and Aunt were righteous,

11:55.030 --> 11:56.360
always helping the weak,

11:56.550 --> 11:57.510
charitable and kind,

11:59.320 --> 12:03.670
yet now their family is massacred.

12:05.910 --> 12:08.030
A line in the story goes,

12:09.030 --> 12:10.910
"You shed blood for the world."

12:11.150 --> 12:13.320
"But now, who remembers?"

12:14.080 --> 12:17.320
The world is full of heartless people;

12:18.510 --> 12:20.320
Jianghu is cruel and unjust.

12:21.286 --> 12:22.160
Better not to join it.

12:23.240 --> 12:24.080
Zhao,

12:26.960 --> 12:28.750
every generation has its own Jianghu.

12:29.000 --> 12:30.960
You have to see for yourself

12:32.120 --> 12:33.870
what it is like.

12:34.240 --> 12:35.440
Your mother is right.

12:38.860 --> 12:41.340
(Grave of Mr. Chang Haosheng)

12:59.840 --> 13:01.510
Ning is so badly injured.

13:01.960 --> 13:02.870
Can he be healed?

13:07.440 --> 13:09.790
Uncle Chang treated us like family.

13:10.790 --> 13:12.630
No matter what, we must heal him

13:13.080 --> 13:13.920
and protect him.

13:15.860 --> 13:18.580
(One month later)

13:32.300 --> 13:37.140
(Bottom of Thousandfold Cliff,
Qingque Sect)

13:39.720 --> 13:40.560
Zhao.

13:51.600 --> 13:53.600
This is the only way in and out
of Qingque Sect.

13:54.080 --> 13:55.720
The cliff is full of traps.

13:55.870 --> 13:56.840
Even birds can't pass.

14:48.360 --> 14:50.030
Water can't flow;

14:51.030 --> 14:53.120
mountains can't be crossed.

14:54.510 --> 14:56.360
Truly, the Thousandfold Cliff.

15:06.200 --> 15:07.120
Trace Butterfly.

15:18.030 --> 15:19.150
Aunt,

15:21.150 --> 15:22.390
it's so beautiful.

15:46.300 --> 15:49.780
(Yang Xiaolan, Siqi Sect)

16:00.630 --> 16:01.670
If you know better,

16:01.670 --> 16:03.960
let me take a bowl of your heart blood.

16:04.320 --> 16:05.440
I won't take your life.

16:05.440 --> 16:06.540
(Qi Lingbo, Qingque Sect)

16:07.510 --> 16:09.960
My poison isn't cleared.

16:10.726 --> 16:11.910
Do you dare to take my blood?

16:12.396 --> 16:14.550
(Dai Fengchi, Qingque Sect)
You just want to bully me.

16:15.320 --> 16:16.510
Stop making excuses.

16:17.360 --> 16:19.080
You took Lingbo's Lotus Pill.

16:19.320 --> 16:20.670
Today, I'll take your heart blood.

16:20.750 --> 16:22.080
If you can, kill me,

16:22.960 --> 16:23.800
or I'll repay you

16:24.630 --> 16:26.080
several times over.

16:28.270 --> 16:29.200
Chang Ning?

16:31.960 --> 16:32.800
Lingbo,

16:33.200 --> 16:34.040
forget it.

16:34.120 --> 16:34.960
If this escalates,

16:35.030 --> 16:36.396
it'll be hard to explain to Master.

16:38.150 --> 16:38.990
Fine.

16:39.943 --> 16:40.870
No need for your blood.

16:44.150 --> 16:45.870
Kowtow 18 times,

16:46.240 --> 16:48.840
and I'll let you off.

16:49.720 --> 16:51.320
18 kowtows?

16:59.270 --> 17:00.440
18 years ago,

17:01.030 --> 17:02.910
your mother was attacked by villains.

17:03.320 --> 17:05.960
My father and Ms. Cai helped her.

17:07.160 --> 17:08.550
17 years ago,

17:08.800 --> 17:10.000
in the battle of good and evil,

17:10.960 --> 17:12.640
my father risked his life

17:13.200 --> 17:15.790
to save the Beichen disciples.

17:16.200 --> 17:17.440
15 years ago,

17:18.270 --> 17:20.920
your father wanted revenge
on your grandfather;

17:21.720 --> 17:23.400
my father

17:23.400 --> 17:24.440
risked everything to help.

17:25.790 --> 17:26.920
Even if I don't mention it,

17:27.590 --> 17:29.400
it doesn't mean you can forget.

17:31.510 --> 17:32.350
Speaking of which,

17:33.590 --> 17:36.070
you should kowtow 18 times to me.

17:36.680 --> 17:37.750
Stubborn, huh?

17:39.550 --> 17:40.720
Make him kneel.

17:59.680 --> 18:01.000
(His injuries are healed.)

18:01.440 --> 18:02.750
(How could he be so weak?)

18:12.030 --> 18:13.590
How lively here.

18:14.200 --> 18:15.720
Not quite as I imagined.

18:17.070 --> 18:18.000
Who are you?

18:18.790 --> 18:20.160
Mind your own business.

18:20.640 --> 18:22.510
We are here to learn.

18:22.720 --> 18:24.200
I'm Yang Xiaolan of Siqi Sect.

18:24.460 --> 18:25.310
She is...

18:25.310 --> 18:26.720
Cai Zhao of Luoying Valley?

18:27.270 --> 18:28.110
You must be

18:28.830 --> 18:30.240
Lingbo.

18:31.200 --> 18:32.590
I've heard Uncle Qi's only daughter

18:32.590 --> 18:33.790
is the No. 1 belle in Beichen.

18:34.400 --> 18:36.790
You indeed have bright eyes and teeth,

18:37.110 --> 18:38.200
icy skin,

18:38.640 --> 18:39.720
delicate hands,

18:40.000 --> 18:40.960
and a peerless figure.

18:41.590 --> 18:43.510
Father always tells me

18:43.510 --> 18:44.610
you're clever and obedient.

18:45.790 --> 18:48.270
I have matters to attend to.

18:49.310 --> 18:50.032
Let Fengchi

18:50.043 --> 18:51.629
take you to the Disciples' Dorm first.

18:51.640 --> 18:53.440
Later, we'll have more time together.

18:54.550 --> 18:55.390
Zhao, Xiaolan,

18:55.640 --> 18:56.480
please.

18:56.960 --> 18:57.800
Zhao,

18:58.270 --> 18:59.110
my father used to say

18:59.160 --> 19:00.920
our families are life-and-death allies.

19:01.680 --> 19:03.240
Unlike them, you surely won't

19:03.400 --> 19:04.350
turn a blind eye to me.

19:04.510 --> 19:05.350
Shut up.

19:05.750 --> 19:07.640
Father brought you here
to heal and seek refuge.

19:07.640 --> 19:08.880
How could you say that?

19:08.880 --> 19:10.200
Chang is still severely injured

19:10.200 --> 19:11.070
and confused.

19:11.510 --> 19:12.400
He might scare Zhao.

19:13.640 --> 19:14.480
Someone.

19:14.720 --> 19:15.570
Yes.

19:15.590 --> 19:17.680
Send Chang back
to Peace Chamber to rest.

19:19.270 --> 19:20.110
I understand.

19:23.400 --> 19:24.680
My family now

19:24.750 --> 19:26.110
has only me left.

19:26.640 --> 19:28.000
The sooner I die, the better.

19:28.790 --> 19:30.030
Then you won't carry the shame

19:30.590 --> 19:31.680
of betraying

19:32.030 --> 19:33.350
or abandoning us.

19:33.920 --> 19:35.030
If you lie again,

19:35.310 --> 19:36.150
I'll kill you.

19:36.270 --> 19:37.110
If you dare,

19:38.200 --> 19:39.240
kill me.

19:46.920 --> 19:49.240
Aren't you also the orphan
raised by Lord Qi?

19:50.680 --> 19:51.750
Being raised,

19:52.000 --> 19:53.200
you've become a lackey.

19:54.720 --> 19:55.750
Then I'll let you have it.

19:57.830 --> 19:58.750
Uncle Qi said

19:58.880 --> 20:00.310
everyone here

20:00.400 --> 20:01.510
treats each other

20:01.680 --> 20:02.720
like family.

20:03.510 --> 20:04.960
Since we are family,

20:05.400 --> 20:06.960
there will inevitably be some disputes.

20:07.920 --> 20:09.030
No need to be so violent.

20:14.143 --> 20:15.163
Father is looking for you.

20:15.550 --> 20:16.390
Chang,

20:16.550 --> 20:17.390
come with me.

20:20.480 --> 20:21.330
Let's go.

20:21.350 --> 20:22.190
Wait.

20:25.750 --> 20:27.880
Since you came to learn,

20:28.200 --> 20:29.270
from now on,

20:29.590 --> 20:30.920
we should get along well.

20:31.550 --> 20:33.070
So, don't meddle

20:33.310 --> 20:34.590
in things you shouldn't.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.920
If it ruins sisterly bonds,

20:37.510 --> 20:40.200
how can we practice together?

20:40.400 --> 20:41.920
You can practice on your own.

20:42.082 --> 20:43.396
I don't like martial arts anyway.

20:43.440 --> 20:44.280
Is that so?

20:45.160 --> 20:46.510
Then why come?

20:46.920 --> 20:47.760
To learn.

20:48.830 --> 20:51.160
Uncle Qi is a renowned gentleman.

20:51.550 --> 20:52.830
Even learning a fraction from him

20:53.310 --> 20:54.750
is a lifelong benefit.

20:55.240 --> 20:56.590
Sharp-tongued

20:56.590 --> 20:58.070
and crafty.

20:58.070 --> 20:58.910
Who taught you

20:58.910 --> 20:59.880
such unruliness?

21:00.110 --> 21:01.000
My aunt.

21:01.920 --> 21:02.566
She said

21:02.577 --> 21:04.310
that there are too many rules
in the world,

21:04.750 --> 21:05.640
but conscience

21:06.110 --> 21:07.880
is more important than rules.

21:08.270 --> 21:10.960
My father and Ms. Cai helped them a lot.

21:11.880 --> 21:12.960
They should kneel

21:12.960 --> 21:13.880
and thank us.

21:14.590 --> 21:15.880
No need to waste words on them.

21:17.030 --> 21:18.200
Heartless scum!

21:18.590 --> 21:19.430
How dare you!

21:19.510 --> 21:21.070
I'll teach you a lesson!

21:22.780 --> 21:23.940
(Song Yuzhi, Qingque Sect)

21:23.960 --> 21:24.880
You promised Master

21:25.310 --> 21:26.720
not to bully Chang.

21:26.920 --> 21:28.160
This is outrageous.

21:28.160 --> 21:29.000
Lingbo.

21:29.960 --> 21:30.800
Lord Song is here.

21:31.300 --> 21:33.660
(Zeng Dalou, Qingque Sect)
Lady Yin wants you.

21:34.270 --> 21:35.110
Alright.

21:44.540 --> 21:45.800
(Dusk Palace)
Zhao,

21:45.880 --> 21:47.830
where did you go just now?

21:48.400 --> 21:50.510
Thousandfold Cliff is picturesque.

21:50.790 --> 21:51.790
I just wandered around.

21:52.110 --> 21:52.950
By chance,

21:53.160 --> 21:54.350
I saw Lingbo

21:54.590 --> 21:56.270
and Chang sparring.

22:08.310 --> 22:09.150
Master.

22:10.160 --> 22:11.000
Lingbo,

22:11.680 --> 22:14.510
did you bully Chang again?

22:14.590 --> 22:15.430
I did not.

22:15.790 --> 22:18.160
We were just exercising

22:18.263 --> 22:19.356
and practicing martial arts.

22:19.590 --> 22:21.160
He isn't fully healed.

22:21.350 --> 22:23.030
How can he exercise?

22:23.040 --> 22:23.880
You...

22:23.900 --> 22:25.920
How can you scold your daughter

22:25.920 --> 22:26.960
without reason?

22:27.790 --> 22:29.440
Lingbo is mischievous,

22:29.680 --> 22:31.200
but she knows her limits.

22:31.943 --> 22:33.880
(Yin Sulian, Lady of Qingque Chief)
Most likely,

22:34.203 --> 22:35.333
those juniors are insensible.

22:36.160 --> 22:37.000
Chang,

22:37.400 --> 22:38.310
right?

22:40.510 --> 22:41.350
Yes.

22:42.110 --> 22:43.680
Lingbo kindly invited everyone

22:44.070 --> 22:45.270
to keep me company

22:45.960 --> 22:46.800
to relieve boredom.

22:48.270 --> 22:49.590
(He swallowed his pride?)

22:50.070 --> 22:51.240
(Very different from earlier.)

22:54.200 --> 22:56.000
These juniors quarrel.

22:56.010 --> 22:56.850
What's the big deal?

22:56.880 --> 22:58.753
(Song Shijun, Guangtian Sect)
We were the same.

23:00.310 --> 23:01.150
No.

23:02.400 --> 23:03.920
We wouldn't allow disciples

23:04.510 --> 23:06.030
to bully the weak.

23:07.510 --> 23:09.400
This child is Chang's only boy,

23:09.720 --> 23:11.070
barely surviving.

23:11.510 --> 23:12.510
Is this the way

23:12.830 --> 23:13.790
you treat him?

23:15.550 --> 23:18.510
Since Yunke brought him back,

23:18.720 --> 23:20.270
he has done everything,

23:20.790 --> 23:22.440
even exhausting his internal power

23:22.750 --> 23:24.550
to expel poison and heal him.

23:25.270 --> 23:26.590
You just don't know that.

23:26.880 --> 23:28.350
Is that why you criticize us now?

23:30.350 --> 23:31.830
With so many disciples,

23:31.960 --> 23:33.200
some are bound to be bad.

23:33.440 --> 23:35.270
We'll train them properly later.

23:36.030 --> 23:36.880
Yunke,

23:37.200 --> 23:38.880
you called Ning here

23:39.070 --> 23:40.510
to discuss his family matters, right?

23:41.070 --> 23:41.910
Yes, yes.

23:46.110 --> 23:46.950
Uncle Cai,

23:47.270 --> 23:48.110
Aunt,

23:48.160 --> 23:49.000
thank you both

23:49.440 --> 23:50.830
for collecting my father's remains

23:52.126 --> 23:53.040
and building a memorial

23:53.240 --> 23:54.510
for the 76 disciples

23:54.960 --> 23:55.800
of Chang Fort.

23:57.600 --> 23:58.440
- Come on.
- Get up.

23:58.440 --> 23:59.280
Get up.

23:59.310 --> 24:00.150
Get up now.

24:00.350 --> 24:01.190
Get up.

24:02.440 --> 24:03.280
Uncle Cai,

24:03.960 --> 24:05.030
any clues to the culprits?

24:05.880 --> 24:07.310
Chang Fort was completely ransacked.

24:07.880 --> 24:09.200
Even the grass was dug up.

24:10.030 --> 24:11.200
They ferreted about.

24:11.750 --> 24:12.680
They seemed

24:13.440 --> 24:14.720
to be looking for something.

24:16.830 --> 24:18.310
It is said that Chang Fort

24:18.590 --> 24:19.790
holds abundant wealth,

24:19.920 --> 24:21.240
with countless rare treasures.

24:21.750 --> 24:22.680
There must be

24:22.920 --> 24:23.960
someone covetous.

24:24.960 --> 24:26.270
The culprit planned meticulously

24:26.510 --> 24:27.510
and acted cruelly.

24:27.920 --> 24:29.790
It's probably not just about money
or treasure.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.200
Could it be

24:35.510 --> 24:36.550
the work of the demon sect?

24:41.640 --> 24:42.680
15 years ago,

24:43.160 --> 24:44.920
Luoying Valley's ambush

24:45.440 --> 24:46.830
wiped out the demon sect elite,

24:47.376 --> 24:48.633
leaving them severely weakened.

24:49.160 --> 24:50.200
They lay dormant for years,

24:50.400 --> 24:52.240
never leaving the Hanhai Mountains.

24:52.590 --> 24:53.680
Now, it seems

24:54.070 --> 24:55.270
they are stirring again.

24:55.310 --> 24:56.270
I remember

24:56.510 --> 24:58.590
Chang Haosheng followed Pingshu,

24:58.590 --> 25:00.440
infiltrating the demon sect
several times.

25:00.750 --> 25:02.000
Could it be that Chang Fort

25:02.000 --> 25:03.590
has some demon sect treasure?

25:04.440 --> 25:05.280
Ning,

25:05.640 --> 25:07.000
has your father ever mentioned

25:07.310 --> 25:08.200
any demon sect treasure

25:08.400 --> 25:10.000
or martial arts manuals?

25:10.070 --> 25:11.070
Are you saying

25:11.750 --> 25:13.270
it's our fault,

25:13.640 --> 25:14.880
deserving this family massacre?

25:15.110 --> 25:15.950
Ning,

25:16.000 --> 25:16.960
I didn't say that.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.000
You are overthinking.

25:19.440 --> 25:21.200
The culprit went to so much trouble

25:21.640 --> 25:22.830
to wipe out the Changs.

25:24.030 --> 25:25.880
There must be a deep grudge.

25:26.200 --> 25:27.440
We must stay alert.

25:27.880 --> 25:28.750
Ning,

25:29.240 --> 25:30.080
rest assured.

25:30.240 --> 25:32.000
I'll help you find the culprit

25:32.920 --> 25:35.350
and give your family justice.

25:43.510 --> 25:44.350
Zhao,

25:44.750 --> 25:46.880
this is the residence
Master arranged for you.

25:58.510 --> 25:59.350
Zhao.

26:01.110 --> 26:02.200
May I ask who you are?

26:02.430 --> 26:04.040
(Fan Xingjia, Qingque Sect)
Fan Xingjia.

26:05.720 --> 26:06.560
Xingjia.

26:08.680 --> 26:09.520
Zhao,

26:09.640 --> 26:11.680
are you satisfied with Chunling Cottage?

26:11.680 --> 26:16.020
(Chunling Cottage)

26:16.240 --> 26:18.030
This must've cost a lot, right?

26:18.270 --> 26:19.510
Indeed.

26:20.510 --> 26:21.690
Come on, Zhao.

26:21.720 --> 26:22.560
Follow me.

26:29.750 --> 26:31.110
The Disciples' Dorm

26:31.110 --> 26:32.350
is far worse

26:32.350 --> 26:33.440
than Chunling Cottage.

26:33.880 --> 26:35.310
Master care

26:35.880 --> 26:37.510
for you

26:38.160 --> 26:39.030
is unmatched.

26:40.400 --> 26:41.790
Master went to great lengths

26:42.240 --> 26:43.750
to keep me here.

26:44.400 --> 26:45.240
Milady.

26:48.160 --> 26:49.070
Milady,

26:49.070 --> 26:50.920
where should I put our luggage?

26:52.030 --> 26:52.870
Follow me.

27:02.640 --> 27:05.310
The Feud Between Nie and Mu?

27:07.110 --> 27:09.960
Mu's Love Affairs?

27:20.510 --> 27:23.310
Han loves reading those things.

27:29.350 --> 27:30.510
I love them.

27:40.020 --> 27:42.380
(Dusk Palace)

27:45.340 --> 27:46.340
(Heroic Legacy)

27:46.350 --> 27:47.510
The Lord is here.

27:51.140 --> 27:54.410
(Heroic Legacy)

27:54.440 --> 27:55.280
Everyone,

27:56.070 --> 27:57.750
being here for our martial training

27:57.750 --> 27:59.000
once every ten years

27:59.920 --> 28:01.160
is a blessing.

28:01.510 --> 28:03.030
I hope you all cherish it.

28:03.590 --> 28:05.440
Each generation has its own Jianghu.

28:06.510 --> 28:07.640
I hope you

28:07.920 --> 28:10.240
inherit the wishes of your predecessors,

28:10.550 --> 28:11.510
upholding justice,

28:11.790 --> 28:12.640
helping the weak,

28:13.240 --> 28:15.160
sweeping away the bad habits,

28:15.510 --> 28:17.000
and establishing new customs,

28:17.350 --> 28:20.030
so that injustices can be righted,

28:20.030 --> 28:21.680
and everyone can make a contribution.

28:22.030 --> 28:23.880
Yes, milord.

28:31.070 --> 28:31.910
From tomorrow,

28:32.200 --> 28:33.206
meditate at the Yin hour,

28:33.610 --> 28:34.900
adjust breathing at the Mao hour,

28:35.080 --> 28:36.240
practice sword at the Si hour,

28:36.440 --> 28:37.460
and rest at the Hai hour.

28:37.720 --> 28:38.560
Meals should be

28:38.720 --> 28:39.880
light and moderate,

28:40.550 --> 28:41.720
no eating after noon.

29:18.790 --> 29:19.630
Zhao,

29:20.640 --> 29:21.510
you are new here.

29:21.510 --> 29:23.310
I have a gift for you as a welcome.

29:26.550 --> 29:27.390
What gift?

29:38.920 --> 29:40.110
It makes a rushing wind sound,

29:40.550 --> 29:41.640
clearly no ordinary item.

29:42.750 --> 29:43.590
Thank you, Lingbo.

29:44.200 --> 29:45.920
Didn't you say
you don't like martial arts?

29:46.400 --> 29:48.000
That doesn't mean I can't fight.

29:48.550 --> 29:51.030
In Jianghu,

29:51.030 --> 29:51.976
all support is unstable.

29:52.110 --> 29:54.240
If you go out
without self-defense skills,

29:54.240 --> 29:55.310
you might get beaten.

29:56.680 --> 29:57.590
Losing is small,

29:58.110 --> 29:59.720
but losing the face of the Qingque Sect

30:00.110 --> 30:01.160
would be a big problem.

30:01.550 --> 30:02.720
Am I right, everyone?

30:09.310 --> 30:10.270
Marvelous moves.

30:13.070 --> 30:14.000
Yuzhi,

30:14.550 --> 30:15.390
she's bullying me.

30:15.880 --> 30:16.920
What's wrong, Yuzhi?

30:17.350 --> 30:18.510
You want to spar with me too?

30:18.880 --> 30:20.440
I've admired Ms. Cai for years.

30:20.640 --> 30:22.160
I want to spar with you

30:22.310 --> 30:23.310
as friends.

30:23.750 --> 30:25.000
If I'm not mistaken,

30:25.640 --> 30:27.030
you two

30:27.030 --> 30:27.870
are engaged, right?

30:28.270 --> 30:29.110
I don't spar

30:29.240 --> 30:31.000
with someone who has a fiancée

30:31.240 --> 30:32.720
to avoid trouble later,

30:33.220 --> 30:34.140
right, Lingbo?

30:34.200 --> 30:35.040
You...

31:32.850 --> 31:34.000
Ning is eccentric

31:34.270 --> 31:35.510
and scheming.

31:35.510 --> 31:37.816
Uncle Chang was gentle and kind.

31:37.950 --> 31:40.310
How could he raise such a son?

31:40.960 --> 31:42.070
You overthink.

31:42.350 --> 31:44.830
I heard when pregnant,

31:44.830 --> 31:45.960
his mother was startled,

31:45.960 --> 31:47.030
suffered insanity.

31:47.700 --> 31:48.550
So, this child

31:48.550 --> 31:50.830
has been weak and sickly since birth,

31:50.830 --> 31:51.960
with asthma.

31:52.586 --> 31:53.790
His life has been hard enough.

31:54.160 --> 31:55.510
So, his temperament isn't good.

31:59.440 --> 32:00.280
Zhao,

32:00.790 --> 32:03.110
this really was arranged by Uncle Qi?

32:05.830 --> 32:06.670
Zhao,

32:07.740 --> 32:08.870
are you too hungry to focus?

32:12.830 --> 32:14.160
I can't

32:14.270 --> 32:15.310
see through Ning.

32:15.750 --> 32:16.830
Father said

32:16.830 --> 32:18.590
Ning is the real one, right?

32:19.110 --> 32:20.590
You've never met Uncle Chang.

32:21.000 --> 32:22.680
How do you know what he's like?

32:23.240 --> 32:24.160
I know.

32:24.440 --> 32:27.440
Father and Mother always say
that after the Battle of Mount Tu,

32:27.640 --> 32:29.766
(Young Chang Haosheng)
Uncle Chang carried Aunt home.

32:30.240 --> 32:31.080
Also,

32:31.750 --> 32:33.550
during the demon sect's attack on us,

32:34.310 --> 32:36.680
Uncle Chang stayed at the entrance alone

32:36.830 --> 32:38.830
for ten days and nights.

32:40.240 --> 32:42.510
Uncle Chang is the best hero.

32:43.030 --> 32:44.270
A hero's son

32:45.680 --> 32:46.960
endured such tragedy.

32:47.000 --> 32:48.510
It's understandable

32:49.590 --> 32:50.720
if his temperament is odd.

32:52.590 --> 32:53.430
If you can,

32:54.510 --> 32:55.440
kill me.

32:59.000 --> 33:00.000
(One face to the public.)

33:00.510 --> 33:01.510
(One face in private.)

33:02.110 --> 33:03.510
Lingbo kindly invited everyone

33:04.350 --> 33:07.070
to keep me company to relieve boredom.

33:09.510 --> 33:12.400
(He even schemed to drag me in.)

33:16.250 --> 33:17.110
Zhao,

33:17.350 --> 33:18.400
my father used to say

33:18.590 --> 33:20.590
our families are life-and-death allies.

33:20.750 --> 33:22.720
Unlike them, you surely won't

33:22.720 --> 33:23.720
turn a blind eye to me.

33:27.440 --> 33:29.070
(This is really strange.)

33:47.270 --> 33:48.110
Ning.

33:49.450 --> 33:50.290
Zhao.

33:52.640 --> 33:54.160
My mother asked me to deliver medicine.

33:55.160 --> 33:56.680
The tendons are stiff.

33:57.000 --> 33:57.920
I'll apply it for you

33:58.110 --> 33:58.950
to stabilize.

33:59.510 --> 34:00.350
It's so late.

34:00.640 --> 34:01.480
I can do it myself.

34:03.750 --> 34:04.590
Fine.

34:06.920 --> 34:08.510
Let me help you.

34:37.710 --> 34:39.200
(He has asthma.)

34:39.710 --> 34:41.360
(Why wear a furry coat?)

34:44.880 --> 34:46.070
I know what you want to ask.

34:47.800 --> 34:48.960
When I was ten,

34:49.440 --> 34:50.800
my asthma was cured.

34:52.250 --> 34:53.680
My father went to great lengths,

34:54.280 --> 34:56.150
bringing Mountain White from Lingnan,

34:56.150 --> 34:57.550
which were very effective.

34:58.510 --> 35:00.710
Uncle Chang's was so thoughtful.

35:01.880 --> 35:03.510
No wonder my aunt always called him...

35:03.710 --> 35:04.550
Nanny Chang.

35:09.440 --> 35:11.710
You've never been in Jianghu,

35:12.510 --> 35:14.070
but your mind is so meticulous,

35:14.510 --> 35:15.510
leaving no missteps.

35:16.030 --> 35:17.190
If you had also seen

35:18.550 --> 35:20.030
your father die

35:20.030 --> 35:21.440
to save you,

35:22.230 --> 35:24.070
and you had to try and survive,

35:24.760 --> 35:27.000
you'd understand why I'm like this.

35:28.510 --> 35:29.350
Who is it?

35:36.520 --> 35:47.180
=Generation to Generation=

36:05.940 --> 36:10.350
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

36:10.915 --> 36:15.530
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

36:15.870 --> 36:20.435
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

36:20.960 --> 36:25.260
♪Free to wander in the world♪

36:28.205 --> 36:32.905
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:33.430 --> 36:37.720
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

36:38.380 --> 36:42.410
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

36:42.725 --> 36:47.850
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

36:48.425 --> 36:53.235
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:53.450 --> 36:57.620
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:58.345 --> 37:02.280
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:02.780 --> 37:08.055
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

37:30.785 --> 37:35.915
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:36.280 --> 37:40.650
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:40.915 --> 37:45.045
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:45.230 --> 37:50.805
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
